Okay so here&#039;s a story
I played a game as Ahri quite sometime ago where I was laneing against a Zed, I won.

after a bit of time the Zed said in all chat &quot;Ahri how many kills do you have?&quot;
Me: &quot;Uhm nine.&quot;
Zed: &quot;How many deaths do I have?&quot;
Me: &quot;Errr one?&quot;
Every other lane had rotated to mid to try and &quot;Help&quot; Zed after I killed him one time and after two failed ganks by Vi.
Which gave me those first nine kills and then I got outta control and started on my bloodlust filled rampage in where I killed the Zed two more times.
My team won and the Vi in post game chat continued to call the Zed a feeder.

His ending score was something like 7/3/2.
I ended the game with something like 18/1/7.
